flowchart TD
  Client[Frontend/Admin/API Clients] --> Security[SecurityConfig + CSRF + Keycloak]
  Security --> Tenant[HttpTenantFilter + TenantResolverService]
  Tenant --> Controllers[Web Controllers]
  Controllers --> Facades[Use-case Facades]
  Facades --> Services[Domain Services]
  Services --> Repositories[JPA Repositories]
  Repositories --> MariaDB[(MariaDB)]
  Facades --> Keycloak[KeycloakService]
  Facades --> RocketChat[RocketChatService]
  Facades --> Matrix[MatrixSynapseService]
  Services --> PeerApis[Generated ORISO Service Clients]
